# Architecture Decision Records

Architectural decisions and their rationale are documented in `docs/architecture/` as numbered ADR files (e.g., `001-push-pull-pattern-divergence.md`).

When working on architectural changes, refactors, or adding new protocols/adapters:

1. Read relevant ADRs in `docs/architecture/` for context on prior decisions
2. Reference ADR recommendations when proposing solutions
3. When a new architectural decision is made, create a new numbered ADR
